ca.mcgill.ecse211.team11

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.team11.Constants

  • public class Constants
extends java.lang.Object
    The Constants class contains all the constants to be used in other classes. This makes adjusting constants during the testing phase easier since all constants are in one location.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
